reviewText: If you missed her in Playboy don't miss her in any movie she has made. The movie shows she is well worth the price you pay.

This is Kira Reed's rarest and most sought after soft erotica films and has been extremely rare in the US and nearly all parts of the world. Now, we are finally able to offer the original English version (with digitally remastered audio) and compatible with all US DVD Players. Excellent Lesbian Content. Madam Savant is a must see for Kira Reed fans.
